      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TYSON NZ (2) has the hoof on the till having been beaten narrowly into second in his last two outings at this circuit and distance, last time working from this mark but fighting well to finish just a neck from the winner. With better luck he is good enough to take out a race like this. FRENCH FRIES (4) finished third when resuming two starts ago then registered a comfortable victory last time out, scoring by 12 metres at this circuit and distance. Has had more than five weeks off but has been kept up to the mark with a trial placing and has the class to win again. ROCK SUPREME (6) switches to a standing start but deserves respect having put together a series of top-three finishes. CALL TO ORDER (7) is back after ten weeks having gone to the paddock off a string of wins and placings. Readied with a solid trial so watch the betting.",
